com.sponsorpay.sdk.android.publisher.mbe.mediation
Class SPMediationAdapter

java.lang.Object
  com.sponsorpay.sdk.android.publisher.mbe.mediation.SPMediationAdapter

public abstract class SPMediationAdapter
extends java.lang.Object

Base class for mobile BrandEngage Mediation adapter

This class defines the required specific methods to every adapter and provides convenience methods handling timeouts, validation and events notifications. The SPMediationCoordinator will communicate the results back to the SPBrandEngageClientz.

videosAvailable

public void videosAvailable(android.content.Context context,
                            SPMediationValidationEvent event,
                            java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> contextData)
Method called from the SPMediationCoordinator to check for videos availability for this provider. The result of the method is returned asynchronously to the provided SPMediationValidationEvent. This method also stores the listener and the context data information to send it back when needed and starts the validation timeout.

Parameters:
context - The activity context
event - The SPMediationValidationEvent to be notified.
contextData - The context data used in this request

startVideo

public void startVideo(android.app.Activity parentActivity,
                       SPMediationVideoEvent event,
                       java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> contextData)
Method called from the SPMediationCoordinator to start videos engagement for this provider. The video status is returned asynchronously to the provided SPMediationVideoEvent. This method also stores the listener and the context data information to send it back when needed and starts the video validation timeout.

Parameters:
parentActivity - The parent activity
event - The SPMediationVideoEvent to be notified.
contextData - The context data used in this request
